OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, A formal consultation has been launched
OL,6, into proposals for new legislation to  
OL,7, ensure stronger protection against     
OL,8, terrorism in public places.            
OL,10,FKnown as Martyn's Law, it is named     
OL,11,Fafter Martyn Hett, one of 22 people    
OL,12,Fkilled in the 2017 Manchester attack.  
OL,14,FThe Home Office said the bill would    
OL,15,Frequire venues to take enhanced steps  
OL,16,Fto help keep the public safe.          
OL,18,FIt said it was seeking views to make   
OL,19,Fsure the new requirements do not place 
OL,20,F"undue burdens" on smaller businesses. 
